-- China Upgrades Chanthu Tropical Storm to Typhoon Level, Forecaster Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-21T10:48:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/china-upgrades-chanthu-tropical-storm-to-typhoon-level-forecaster-says.html

          
          
             China raised its alert on tropical
storm Chanthu to typhoon level, the National Meteorological
Center said in a statement on its website today. Chanthu may
make landfall in southern China tomorrow and will bring heavy
rain to Guangdong and Hainan provinces, the center said.  
